{"tid":522202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭頂...  66歲丈夫擸刀跟蹤入便利店 35歲妻被割面毀容","createTime":"2018-01-07T10:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T00:09:07.000Z","uid":72009,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7f8d57a7d6da51b1183e450c2c99048570640dee","tid":522202,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"消息稱，疑犯與傷者為夫婦關係，據悉女方於去年9月申請離婚，今日疑犯跟蹤妻子到上址，雙方一度發生爭執。<br />\n【17:10】警方於景峰徑一個草叢撿獲相信是案中的利刀<br />\n<br />\n屯門新墟井財街11A號OK便利店，下午2時半發生傷人血案。一名66歲姓黃男子在便利店內，以利刀襲擊一名35歲姓廖女子的臉部，逞兇後立即逃走，便利店女職員見狀報警求助。衝鋒隊警員接報趕至現場展開追截，約100米外看見疑犯將一把利刀棄於草叢，警員追至安定邨輕鐵站外終將疑犯制服拘捕。廖女面及頸受傷，由救護車送往醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，疑犯與傷者為夫婦關係，據悉女方於去年9月申請離婚，今日疑犯跟蹤妻子到上址，雙方一度發生爭執。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180107/large/1515319644_40dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180107%2Flarge%2F1515319644_40dc.jpg&h=745d6196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已估到劇情"},{"pid":"a6ff30d93ddecd8ebd8b83adc9f08145718b4463","tid":522202,"uid":4780,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"支那女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd592209ce80d7a51d15accc374a0f5d8f8c028f","tid":522202,"uid":456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:25:34.000Z","msg":"點樣由景峰追到去安定呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好遠下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad6ecac8e82e417d42994b603d6080961c1f7a7","tid":522202,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:26:59.000Z","msg":"廢老唔對<br />\n佢有俾你屌"},{"pid":"c77f32bc3d6d65165a39e0d00023cf8dd7178c0f","tid":522202,"uid":675